dct_title_s: Port Papudo : Horcon and Quintero Bays
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. In upper margin: South America. Coast of Chile by the officers of H.M.S. Beagle 1835. Historic Maps copy has label on verso: South America. Port Papudo, and Horcon and Quintero Bays. 1300. Historic Maps copy has ms. annotations.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Published according to Act of Parliament at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty, Augt. 18th, 1840.
